gnm:Cells.gnm:Cell: This table is the solution of tunnel tracking.
DATA sheet - contains the results of tunnel circles (R1-R8) surveys and basic calculations.
OLS sheet - contains the solution of the normal equations of the tunnel prediction problem.
MPLU sheet - contains the inversion of a matrix using PLU decomposition.
MQR sheet - contains the inversion of a matrix using QR decomposition.
MLL sheet - contains the inversion of a symmetric matrix using LL decomposition.
OUTPUT sheet - contains the tunnel prediction.
CIRCLE sheet - contains the circle prediction.
HOW TO: For the correct operation of the forecast, it is necessary to accumulate the results of at least 10 tunnel circles.
